{"id": "1500745746595582112", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "412620054878879745", "author_name": "mmm64n", "author_bot": false, "content": "今高難易度2-10と通常ストーリー6-10で詰まり始めているのですが、密約強化と札凸、キャラ凸、スキル、どれを優先した方が良いでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T06:27:48.496000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-04T06:42:24.789000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1500746629748359239", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "412620054878879745", "author_name": "mmm64n", "author_bot": false, "content": "マーフィー・ゴリアテ・ファイント・ソレールで何度か試したのですが、ソレールは札が無いのと、深海は後々辛いとお見かけしたので…", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T06:31:19.056000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1500772868382916710", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "恒常素材クエストにスタミナ使うのは罠なのでスタミナは欲しい密約以外は全部イベントに回してください。\n\n今回のイベだと最終ステージ開けたらスタミナ回復剤ぶっ込んでもいいやつです。", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T08:15:34.834000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["888985306194407434"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1500699478129115187", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1500779458854916108", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "797763912300625950", "author_name": "kasinoramune", "author_bot": false, "content": "参考になるかは分かりませんが、6-10クリア時のパーティです。\n当時はスキルを優先していました。\n反撃が結構刺さる相手かと思いますので、遺物「イラクサのベスト」を優先的に取ってみるといいかもしれません。", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T08:41:46.125000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["412620054878879745"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1500779458888597655", "filename": "Screenshot_20260504-172241.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1325910, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1500779458888597655/Screenshot_20260504-172241.png?ex=6a33af4a&is=6a325dca&hm=dd01551d1d00a78934e21b96c6f061671cba99a42416e292998a2141b0195002&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1500745746595582112", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1500780216811786321", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "888985306194407434", "author_name": "mas65100", "author_bot": false, "content": "そうなんすか結構使っちゃってました", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T08:44:46.836000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["797509921343275038"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1500772868382916710", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1500780259010809886", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "888985306194407434", "author_name": "mas65100", "author_bot": false, "content": "気をつけて集めます", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T08:44:56.897000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1500797018430378024", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "どの強化で劇的に変わるとかは多分無いかな？と思います。\nただ、キャラ凸についてはファイントをよく使うなら２凸まではそこそこオススメですね！\nあとは守秘者のレベルによる体力とか遺物の効果アップなんかもあるので、コツコツやっていけば自然と楽になるとは思います。", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T09:51:32.654000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["412620054878879745"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1500745746595582112", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1500797357183205477", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "先ほど試しに6-10をやってきましたが、マフィ、ゴニキ、ファイント、ソレールで組んでこんな感じです", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T09:52:53.419000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-04T09:57:21.513000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1500797355769987243", "filename": "Screenshot_20260504-184652.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1476009, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1500797355769987243/Screenshot_20260504-184652.png?ex=6a33bff5&is=6a326e75&hm=af319bf4c8035f5dad76ccea38d9a9f7fe721a1b9815f16644ef548d298674bf&"}, {"id": "1500797356273307728", "filename": "Screenshot_20260504-184711.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1285599, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1500797356273307728/Screenshot_20260504-184711.png?ex=6a33bff5&is=6a326e75&hm=06442a50e344b96698ef1439a69e12966d5b06f6f97ec70e04ea12160df93504&"}, {"id": "1500797356852117534", "filename": "Screenshot_20260504-184719.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1430464, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1500797356852117534/Screenshot_20260504-184719.png?ex=6a33bff5&is=6a326e75&hm=df57de112adc8e41ba28342359038df9b523a1285ea300aafd3cbe581a889479&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1500798403184037922", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "このゲームって攻撃や防御のカードが基本的に弱いんですが、狂気やキーチャを貯める為にも使わざるを得ないので刻印とかで補ってあげるのを意識すると多少は楽になるかと思います。", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T09:57:02.805000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
